    <note>Mou(1) Zicai [20742] I am assuming that Zicai made the move to Huzhou, but it could have been his father, Xigui [20741]. Son, Yan [20743], was the first member of the family explicitly identified as a Huzhou resident emigre from Jingyan county. Zicai denounced Jia(3) Sidao and retired from the civil service. CBD, 1, 641-2.</note>
